comes to masters.

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.020
So if you're going
to get your master's

00:01:53.020 --> 00:01:56.040
of engineering here in Course 6.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:58.460
And you want to do it in game
design or game development,

00:01:58.460 --> 00:02:01.460
and you need a mentor,
we can be your mentor.

00:02:01.460 --> 00:02:05.160
We also host a lot of
events and outreach events

00:02:05.160 --> 00:02:06.026
and guest lectures.

00:02:06.026 --> 00:02:08.400
