01:23:44.960 --> 01:23:48.430
compiler for Flash, called
Flex, that you can download

01:23:48.430 --> 01:23:51.630
for Linux, Mac, and PC.

01:23:51.630 --> 01:23:54.500
However, there is also
this licensed version,

01:23:54.500 --> 01:23:57.580
which you can download
for a 30-day trial,

01:23:57.580 --> 01:23:59.920
called Flash Builder.

01:23:59.920 --> 01:24:04.350
Unfortunately for Mac
users in particular,

01:24:04.350 --> 01:24:09.060
