01:29:14.775 --> 01:29:16.900
to build on, because of
all the browser differences

01:29:16.900 --> 01:29:17.733
and stuff like that.

01:29:17.733 --> 01:29:19.110
But it is certainly possible.

01:29:19.110 --> 01:29:21.279
I recommend if you
