01:41:31.270 --> 01:41:32.520
I might be planning.

01:41:32.520 --> 01:41:34.270
That's going to be part of it.

01:41:34.270 --> 01:41:35.140
I might be thinking.

01:41:35.140 --> 01:41:38.180
But there's something that's
distracting me for thinking.

01:41:38.180 --> 01:41:40.600
Maybe I have to make
actions really, really fast.

01:41:40.600 --> 01:41:43.430
Or I can make actions and I can
think a long period of time.

01:41:43.430 --> 01:41:45.450
All that is the
big wide spectrum

01:41:45.450 --> 01:41:47.610
of what we're talking
about with strategy games.

