01:53:51.270 --> 01:53:52.840
in your games.

01:53:52.840 --> 01:53:55.690
Be prepared for your choices
not to be interesting.

01:53:55.690 --> 01:53:59.050
Try to iterate through them
and make them more interesting.

01:53:59.050 --> 01:54:01.192
But we don't have a ton
of time to really help

01:54:01.192 --> 01:54:02.900
you make the greatest
games in the world.

01:54:02.900 --> 01:54:03.400
Right?

01:54:03.400 --> 01:54:05.725
So we want your choices
